   <text>
      <body>

         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1655_brd_ncd_i_r.jpg"/>

         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>الله اکبر</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div1" xml:id="trans_div1">
            <p>God is great</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>متصدیان مهمات و معاملات پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               را انهاء آنکه چون مطیع الاسلام
               <lb/><persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرشوتم داس</persName>
                در باب فرزندان
                <persName ref="#chandarBhan">چندربهان</persName>
                وجه پیشکش و حواله داشتن از حضور مبلغ
               <measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="4000">چهار هزار روپیه</measure>
               <lb/> بدرگاه والاجاه بخدمت متصدیان حضور عرضه داشت نموده بود این مقدمات را وزارت و
               اقبال پناه
               <lb/>وکالت و اجلال و دستگاه مدارالمهامی
               <persName ref="#dianatKhan">دیانتخان</persName>
               بعرض باریافتهای مجلس قدس مشاکل رسانید
               <lb/>حسب الامر جلیل القدر مقرر شد که از نوشته متصدیان جاگیر صوبه
               <placeName ref="#malwa">مالوه</placeName>
               ظاهر شد که اگر
               <measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="4000">چهار هزار روپیه</measure>
               <lb/>بر پیشکش گرفته شود باعث جلاء وطن فرزندان
               <persName ref="#chandarBhan">چندربهان</persName>
               میگردد و زر بوصول نمیرسد
               پروانه باسم چودری
               <lb/><persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتمداس</persName>
               صادر گردد که مبلغ چهارهزار روپیه را معاف داشتم تلافی و تدارک این احسان
               <lb/>باید که در حاصل آمده شود و از قرار واقع دولتخواهی شما ظاهر گردد که در عوض خدمت
               چودهرایی<note>From here, the main text continues into the margin.</note>
               <lb/>مرحمت میشود بموجب پروانه عملنموده شده باید که
               <lb/><unclear>جستن</unclear>
               سعی خدمت خود را پرسوتمداس بنوعی که
               <lb/>در پروانه حضور قید است بعمل آورد که ظاهر گردد خدمت
               <lb/>را بموجب ایشان عالیشان سعی نموده گرفته خواهد شد و در خدمت خود
               <lb/>ساعی و سرگرم باشد و آزادی امیدواری تمام در زراعت و آبادانی بکوشد
               <lb/>درینباب نهایت تاکید دانسته زیاده از این مبالغه نطلبند 
               <lb/>تحریر فتاریخ 
               <date calendar="#julus">
                  غره شهر ربیع الثانی   
                  سنه
                  <num>۲۸</num>
                  جلوس
               </date>
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div2" xml:id="trans_div2">
            <p><lb/>To the officials of the affairs and business of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName> it is declared that since the Obedient to Islam
               <lb/>
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>
                had petitioned<note>The phrase used is '<ref type="glossary" target="#gl_arzdasht">ʿarzdasht</ref> numuda'.</note>the officials of
               the exalted court
               <lb/>on behalf of the sons<note><persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> was not <persName ref="#chandarBhan">Chandar Bhan's</persName> son, but his
                  nephew. The term used, farzandan, is sometimes broadly construed and may have included <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>.</note> of <persName ref="#chandarBhan">Chandar Bhan</persName> [regarding] the obligation of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pishkash">pishkash</ref> and the transfer
               of the sum of
               <measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="4000">4000 rupees</measure>, this matter was referred by the Refuge of Ministry and Glory
               <lb/>and Representation
               <persName ref="#dianatKhan">Dianat Khan</persName>
                to the members of the heavenly assembly [officers of the exalted court].
               <lb/>It was ordered that from the writing of the officers of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jagir">jagir</ref> of
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_suba">suba</ref> <placeName ref="#malwa">Malwa</placeName>, it has become clear that if
               <measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="4000">four thousand rupees</measure>
               <lb/>were to be seized as <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pishkash">pishkash</ref>, this will
               cause the exile of the children of
               <persName ref="#chandarBhan">Chandar Bhan</persName>
                and the money will not be collected. [Thus] the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">parvana</ref> is issued in the name
               of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref>
               <lb/>
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>
               that I excuse the sum of <measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="4000">four thousand rupees</measure>. For this kindness,
               <lb/>all collections should be made and your loyalty should become obvious since
               in exchange the office of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri"
                  >chaudhri</ref>.
               <lb/>should be granted [to you]. Work should be done according to the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">parvana</ref>. 
               <lb/>It is necessary that <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> makes efforts of service according to the  
               <lb/>[details] of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">parvana</ref> of the Lord so that it becomes obvious that the service 
               <lb/>is according to the order and the best effort is made. Be engaged in your 
               <lb/>own service, and make all efforts in the cultivation and population [of the area]. 
               <lb/>Know this matter to be settled. More effort than this is not called for. 
               <lb/>Written on the <date calendar="#julus">first of Rabiʿ al-sani in the year 28 of the reign</date>.
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further.</g>
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further.</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned><gap/>
               <persName ref="#muradBakhsh">مراد بخش</persName>
                  سنه
                  <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">۱۰۶۵</date>
                   </mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div3" xml:id="trans_div3">
            <p>
               <stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned><gap/>
                  <persName ref="#muradBakhsh">Murad Bakhsh</persName>
                  <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">1065</date></mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div>

         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1655_brd_ncd_i_v.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               <date calendar="#julus">بتاریخ ۲ شهر ربیع الثانی سنه ۲۸</date>
               <lb rend="empty"/>نقل بدفتر رسید 
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
               <unclear>د</unclear>
               </p>
         </div>
         
         <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="trans_div4">
            <p> 
               On the <date calendar="#julus">2nd of the month of Rabiʿ al-sani in the year 28</date>,
               <lb rend="empty"/>the copy reached the office. <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further</g>.<note>The precise meaning of the letter underneath the note is not clear.</note>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
